RTCRemoteInboundRtpStreamStatsTransportI.summary: The transportId property of the dictionary is a string that uniquely identifies the associated statistics object for this RTP stream's underlying transport.

remarks.para: RTCRemoteInboundRtpStreamStats and RTCTransportStats objects are correlated by iterating the to find the statistics objects where RTCRemoteInboundRtpStreamStats.transportId is equal to .

RTCRemoteInboundRtpStreamStatsTransportI.value: A string that contains the of the object that was inspected to produce the object associated with this RTP stream.
